text: Southeast of Saline USD 306 is a public unified school district headquartered approximately 4 miles west of Gypsum, Kansas, United States. The district includes the communities of Assaria, Bridgeport, Gypsum, Kipp, Mentor, and nearby rural areas. ==Schools== The school district operates the following schools: * Southeast of Saline Junior-Senior High School, west of Gypsum * Southeast of Saline Elementary School, west of Gypsum ==See also== * List of unified school districts in Kansas * List of high schools in Kansas * Kansas State Department of Education * Kansas State High School Activities Association ==References== ==External links== * Category:School districts in Kansas Category:Education in Saline County, Kansas
